Get data aggregate

Source: R/get_data_aggregate.R
get_data_aggregate.Rd

Get data aggregate

get_data_aggregate(
  system_id = as.numeric(Sys.getenv("TIGO_ID")),
  datetime_min = Sys.time() - 7 * 24 * 3600,
  datetime_max = Sys.time(),
  level = "min",
  sensors = TRUE,
  params = c("Pin", "Vin", "Iin", "RSSI"),
  header = "key",
  tz = ""
)

Arguments

system_id

ID of the system (integer), (default: as.numeric(Sys.getenv("TIGO_ID")))
datetime_min

Start datetime of data (default: Sys.time() - 7243600)
datetime_max

End datetime of data (default: Sys.time())
level

"min" (minute ) or "day" (aggregates), default: "min"
sensors

Whether to include sensor data TRUE/FALSE (default: TRUE)
params

Type of data to return (default: c("Pin", "Vin", "Iin", "RSSI"))
header

either "id" or "key" header (default: "key")
tz

time zone of system (default: "")

Value

list with data
